cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper focuses on deep learning methods for image classification and object detection, which are commonly studied in the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) fields. The use of adaptive structural learning in the Deep Belief Network (DBN) also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the evaluation of the proposed method on a benchmark data set suggests a potential focus on multimedia (cs.MM) as well.
